{
  "stem": "471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think he went on once and he testified for him too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, from Schindler, from the Plaszow, we went to Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then to Brinnlitz, another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He has no authority.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He has no power.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I'm not sure that he said, even he doesn't carry a gun in the morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they let him out for a few days or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went by.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Believe you me, before he was husky, big.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came out skinny, like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like you see him on the-- you're going to see him in the picture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wasn't the same, Goth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He probably got, you know, a good investigation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a way, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But everybody you know, has to say-- take off their hat when he walk by.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, give him their respect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you're afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to certain people, he said, no power.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He has no authority.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't worry about anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're not going to do anything here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was close to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes you know, he walked by like I-- like I'm sitting next to you here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he'd walk by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He ask how you doing?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Never complained.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a closest-- a [? co-accident ?] with Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Schindler once.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She-- there came once a big truck with bread, full of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they called me to unload the bread to the warehouse, from the truck to the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was carry like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are-- naturally, we were supervised by the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The SS was watching us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were watching that nobody steals it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She blink with her eyes on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
